, slavery or forced labour. (有關新彊嘅指控三樣都有)<br />\n<br />\n如果係咁第二句就 可以直入指呢位傑出校友其實係反對你呢啲 ethics, 唔參與唔接受強迫勞動 policy: <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">But as a distinguished Kingston alumni he seemed to be against your University's explicit commitment &quot;to the highest standards of ethical conduct in all our activities&quot;, and the policy of not to &quot;engage in, or condone, the practices of human trafficking, slavery or forced labour.</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;fast forward&quot; 其實無乜意思, 其實都唔駛講<br />\n<br />\npolitical stance  人人可以唔同, 你插佢呢個無乜用, 但上邊啲 ethical value 就唔同, 可以普世啲...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T19:50:24.000Z","msg":"唔該晒巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我聽朝起身改先"},{"pid":"c0450ccf661f8b15ad0207ee6747c3d740ab5cf9","tid":2463024,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439942f2e065cb5161c258925ff3e0f2030941df","tid":2463024,"uid":205232,"like":5,"dislike":83,"score":-78,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"救李宇軒好過啦 浪費資源 手足不是condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T19:52:24.000Z","msg":"blocked"},{"pid":"52553a73e2050919e330b4da388439e383a53b89","tid":2463024,"uid":309049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T20:00:47.000Z","msg":"Eason應該會好唔開心，仲有佢老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為錢對Eason黎講已經唔算得d咩，但佢攞呢個學位果陣睇得出佢真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢老豆係Eason 攞呢個學位果陣同Eason講過，話Eason果陣大學冇畢業，欠佢一個學位，而家終於叫補返個學位"},{"pid":"d88ca8f6820d5c80a2b38baa767f10001becae55","tid":2463024,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T21:22:54.000Z","msg":"玩咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n